  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Les Arolles is on a half board basis. </p>
<p>A continental breakfast buffet with additional hot options is served between 7:30-9:30 am. A late breakfast is also served at the bar until 11am.</p>
<p>Après ski snacks and afternoon tea including cakes and hot drinks are served from 4:30pm to keep you going until dinner.</p>
<p>Dinner is served in buffet style four course evening meals and is served between 7-9pm. Free water, wine and fruit juices are included and there'll be show cooking -  you can expect a variety of themed and Savoyard speciality menus each evening.</p>
<p>Free upgrade to all inclusive for departures 22nd, 29th Mar &amp; 5th Apr 25 is valid for all room types. This includes full board, fruit juice, hot drinks, a draft beer and a selection of alcoholic beers.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
