  <description><![CDATA[<p>Renovated in a contemporary style, Hotel Les Arolles offers a modern take on mountainous atmosphere and is placed in the heart of the highest ski resort of <a data-udi="umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8}" title="Val Thorens">Val Thorens</a>. </p>
<h2>Fantastic location </h2>
<p>A usual crowd pleaser for keen skiers, Les Arolles is located on the side of the piste and is close to the Campagnoles and Musaraignes lifts so hitting the slopes early to explore the <a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">Three Valleys ski area</a> couldn't be easier. If you're new to the sport, the ski and board school meeting area is only a short 2-3 minute walk away and the nearby magic carpet lifts are also ideal if you're looking to put in some extra practice after your lessons.</p>
<h2>Great for groups </h2>
<p>Hotel Les Arolles is a great option if you and you party are looking for great value for money with a touch of luxury. We're sure you'll make the most of the large bar area and south facing terrace for some après ski fun after a fulfilling day in the snow. The hotel also offers interconnecting rooms with separate sleeping areas for added peace of mind.</p>
<h2>Relaxation facilities </h2>
<p>What better way to rejuvenate for another day on the slopes than visiting the spa. Open everyday, except Saturday morning, you'll have access to the benefits of a sauna, whirlpool baths and hammam. Or go the extra mile and immerse yourself in a massage or beauty treatment that uses a selection of natural cosmetic products that are all locally produced in France - whatever takes your fancy.</p>
<h3>Why is this is an Inghams' Choice property?</h3>
<p><strong>Great location</strong> - Located on the side of the piste and only a short distance from the lifts and magic carpets,  guests staying at the Hotel Les Arolles can enjoy easy access onto the Three Valleys Ski Area.</p>
<p><strong>Evening entertainment</strong> - Cosy up for an evening in at the lovely hotel lounge and bar which often has a live pianist, share your stories from your day on the mountain with a delicious cocktail and marvel at the mountains surrounding you.</p>
<p><strong>Wellness area</strong> - After a day of exploring the mountain, there is nowhere better to be than relaxing in the wellness facilities which include a whirlpool, sauna and hammam  - the Hotel Les Arolles ticks all your holiday boxes for a true winter escape.</p>]]></description>
